Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何{\rsymbol}…{\r}什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发现 从这里能望到岛上的实验场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想确认要不要封锁一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看得到铁塔 但无法直接观察实验场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不必封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南条特务中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为实在太漂亮了 想让左文字先生也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方还有好多 下次再带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尘归尘 土归土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色悲剧要归为无吗{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立个墓碑又有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将抹不去的恐惧 用喧嚣和享乐掩盖的{\rsymbol}…{\r}虚伪城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类只有这种时候显得格外干练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道的人永远记得就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少明白你还没忘 我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始本 托你件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去查查船为什么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有蹊跷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以等你吧 元帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐{\rsymbol}…{\r}曾在这里呆过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者的升级如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束后 经铃城曹长批准
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带哈兹福特小姐来了岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去路上 偶然间发现了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长您呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友介绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里景色好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田他们正在准备接收物资
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回野营地做搬入准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有联络 卡普少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 传令第四大队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫鲁姆斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里希特霍芬发来联络
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已成功潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您觉得这不妥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个白痴准将
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然借里希特霍芬去参与这种行动{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽做些无聊事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配合前方的总攻击 从背后奇袭扰敌{\rsymbol}…{\r}吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说最近确实进军缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这招也真够大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}下下签啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然抽到 就要做好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是干啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你想光着屁股在城里冲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你可饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务中别没大没小的 托马斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失敬了 托格尔斯军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伍长说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关卡的工作人员已经买通 不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城里有阿兰达斯的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小规模的独立部队为做补给在附近野营了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 他们坏不了事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快给我弄完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接到补给 正往这边赶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估计快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来之后抓紧装货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始本先生来联络过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒没什么值得注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们见面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阔别多年啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是呢{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直挺担心他离开军队后过得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来依旧硬朗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他依旧那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要确认敌人动向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去联络大队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 为什么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿都回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 疗养温泉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都拿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随后我们要向格维茨平原转移
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前线有动作 可能很快会发起总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 快点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈尔米亚要装货?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那条船晚点的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于货物清单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是工业机械配件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卸货之后放在附近工厂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这工厂的拥有者叫戈尔吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这有名的因戈尔米亚拥护者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后才是有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈尔吉的工厂有三台工业用机械 已经向上面申请出货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通关时间 预计是今晚20点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:10:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寺井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫席加行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面再道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让我把头发等白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席加先生出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好 注意力集中点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思维脉冲驱动装置 GO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传感阵列 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认环境信息统合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵装扩展 激活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 全系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能光琢磨姐姐那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了这 就只等着踢那群混蛋的屁股了吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 托马斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事少瞎通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曳战者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:13:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就阻截这一点上值得表扬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说其他都够呛哦 时宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知总部 总攻时间后移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们清除障碍后 再继续计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你碍事 新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总部决定中止计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们立刻撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划还可以继续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我告诉总部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 动作变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 上升的不是机师水平 而是机体反应性能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止奇袭的目的已经达成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必过分追击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是没想追 可对面{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 不是撤退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能丢下少尉不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位请看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在缓冲地带贝尔哈罗斯的海岸 此刻正发生战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海岸虽然不是非战斗区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不知损害何时会波及贝尔哈罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 美丽的贝尔哈罗斯市也会成为战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让这种事发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我家元帅在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把赤影派到能看见桥的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现万一就把桥炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳伦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟{\rsymbol}…{\r}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋们 居然把托马斯{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗机 被压制中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲 前去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到此为止了 新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托格尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 请快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型机{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有里希特霍芬一人 成功撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去回收
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微{\rsymbol}…{\r}冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格维茨平原上敌人已停止动作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战况没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因意外情况计划紧急中止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估计不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是那个{\rsymbol2}「{\r}意外情况{\rsymbol2}」{\r}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时宗的直觉果然对了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说他们也是军人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然是因戈尔米亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺厉害嘛 联动深度17
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与银色歼灭者连接的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说这个 等于考试17分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开了几星期 已经不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得比之前灵活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说今天才第一次{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得真正战斗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都毁了啊 吉米喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 别这样 不要在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是对你来说这里更重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐的{\rsymbol}…{\r}那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后一段时间{\rsymbol}…{\r}我会尽力做自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在姐姐最后留下照片的地方 我真正战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的事我将来一定会查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在先{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这样也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}约定
