Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:19.38,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:21.89,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:26.70,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… あの火は仲間か?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.45,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:36.94,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.82,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:46.63,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:51.77,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:57.02,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:01.59,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.84,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:07.22,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.85,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.40,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:23.16,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.90,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Break up foreordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:28.66,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.82,0:00:06.00,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 向着这无望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.62,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志将一飞冲天
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.89,0:00:26.70,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是战友吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.96,0:00:31.45,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}当走之路是黑暗吗{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.05,0:00:36.94,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光闪动
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.82,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无名感情在胸中翻涌
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.01,0:00:46.63,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此时此刻在此地 尚不能结束-
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.63,0:00:51.77,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那么就做好活下去的准备吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.89,0:00:57.02,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔热忱 越积越高无处释放
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.02,0:01:01.59,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}这份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.97,0:01:07.22,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}战场之上 笑谈青涩有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.85,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我会一个一个亲自去实践
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.03,0:01:15.40,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放马过来{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:27.48,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見渡す世界 足はすくむけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:31.35,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}歩みを止めぬビリーバー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:36.02,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}幾度の傷 痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:41.25,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一筋の強き意思見つける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:46.10,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}戸惑いに揺れる心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:51.04,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}足取りは覚束なくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.64,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}恐れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:59.25,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}希望へと両手伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:04.56,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}通り抜ける 願い纏う風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:09.78,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}迷わない瞳はただ前を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:15.25,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}共に行けば 絶望など他愛ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:20.31,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重い闇さえ 振り払うだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:24.84,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸を震わせる未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}誓って
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.21,0:22:27.48,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}放眼整个世界 即便双脚在颤抖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.34,0:22:31.35,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸怀信念之人也不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.62,0:22:36.02,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}无数次受伤 无数次疼痛中
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.02,0:22:41.25,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那股强韧的意志映入眼帘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.33,0:22:46.10,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}迷惑中动摇的心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.53,0:22:51.04,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}即便步履已经蹒跚
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.64,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}也绝不畏惧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.97,0:22:59.25,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}向着希望 努力伸出双手
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.82,0:23:04.56,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}清风吹过 带来一份祈愿
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.66,0:23:09.78,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}坚定不移的瞳孔 只看前路
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.21,0:23:15.25,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}与你同行 绝望又算得上什么
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.41,0:23:20.31,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}再沉重的黑暗 也能一挥而散
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.58,0:23:24.84,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未来必定振奋人心
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.20,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我保证
